## 5. curl API 测试命令

### 5.1 创建会话 (admin)

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/sessions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${ADMIN_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"scope":"dashboard","title":"招聘数据概览咨询"}'
# Response: 201 Created
# {"id":"sess-001","scope":"dashboard","title":"招聘数据概览咨询","status":"active",...}
```

### 5.2 获取 Context (hrbp)

```bash
curl -X GET "http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/context?scope=job&scopeId=job-001" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${HRBP_TOKEN}"
# Response: 200 OK
# {"context":{...},"citations":[{...}]}
```

### 5.3 发送消息 (recruiter)

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/chat \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"sessionId":"sess-001","message":"当前招聘漏斗转化率如何？","scope":"funnel","scopeId":"job-001"}'
# Response: 200 OK
# {"message":{"id":"msg-001","role":"assistant","content":"...","humanReviewStatus":"pending",...}}
```

### 5.4 无权限请求 (business_owner)

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/chat \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${BUSINESS_OWNER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"sessionId":"sess-001","message":"test","scope":"dashboard"}'
# Response: 403 Forbidden
# {"error":"Forbidden","message":"You do not have permission to access AI Copilot"}
```

### 5.5 人工审查接受

```bash
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/messages/msg-001/review \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"action":"accepted"}'
# Response: 200 OK
# {"message":{"humanReviewStatus":"accepted"},...}
```

### 5.6 人工审查编辑

```bash
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/messages/msg-001/review \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"action":"edited","editedContent":"修正后的回答..."}'
# Response: 200 OK
```

### 5.7 人工审查拒绝

```bash
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/messages/msg-001/review \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"action":"rejected","reason":"信息不准确"}'
# Response: 200 OK
```

### 5.8 生成草稿动作

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/draft-action \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}" \
  -d '{"sessionId":"sess-001","messageId":"msg-001","actionType":"schedule_interview","params":{"candidateId":"cand-001","suggestedDate":"2026-07-01"}}'
# Response: 201 Created
```

### 5.9 确认草稿动作

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/copilot/draft-action/da-001/confirm \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${RECRUITER_TOKEN}"
# Response: 201 Created
# {"action":{"id":"act-001",...},"draftAction":{"status":"confirmed"}}
```

